{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban abortions after 12 weeks",
        "additional_details": "There are alternatives people can turn to if they do not want their child. There are many people who can\u2019t have children and who would be over the moon to be able to raise a child. Stop allowing abortions after 12 weeks \u2013 we believe every child deserves a chance in life.",
        "background": "Ban abortions after 12 weeks. Babies can survive after 21 weeks, and we believe it is wrong to be able to have an abortion after 12 weeks. ",
